│ Here, the *first transformation* means the *first transformation point* that modifies the IR in the pass         │
│ regardless of whether it's in the `autofix/build/llvm-build/107171/bin/opt -p loop-vectorize -mattr=+v -S        │
│ /tmp/reprod_a63eh26b.l` module or other modules.                                                                 │
